      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが星見プロに移籍して",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しばらく経ったある日",
      "startTime": 3.459999962510734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お休みなのに\n時間をいただいてすみません……",
      "startTime": 8.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ、俺も休日の方が時間が取れるし",
      "startTime": 12.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そう言っていただけると助かります……",
      "startTime": 16.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ",
      "startTime": 19.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は相談があるってことだけど……\nなんだか元気ないな。深刻なことなのか？",
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、{user}さんにとっては\nそんなに大したことじゃないんです！",
      "startTime": 31.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ちょっと私……\n芸能界引退しようかなって……あはは……",
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大したことじゃないか！",
      "startTime": 41.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなによろけたら\n危ないですよ",
      "startTime": 44.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが怪我なんてしたら\n星見プロは大変です",
      "startTime": 48.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "君が引退する方がもっと大変だよ！\nLizNoirのライブもようやく決まったのに",
      "startTime": 53.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ホントーに、すみません！　次のライブは\n莉央さん、葵さん、こころの三人体制で……",
      "startTime": 61.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "何があったんだ？　詳しく話してくれ\nもしかして、またこころに変なこと言われたとか――",
      "startTime": 68.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、こころは私にそんなこと絶対言いませんよ\nレッスンでアドバイスもしてくれますし",
      "startTime": 77.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "一応言うけど、腹筋1000回ってこころに言われても\nしなくてもいいからな？",
      "startTime": 83.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、それはもう冗談だって分かってます\n代わりに腕立て伏せが1000回になりました",
      "startTime": 89.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それもウソというか、冗談だよ……",
      "startTime": 93.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "愛は素直過ぎだ……。辞めたいのはレッスンが\nキツ過ぎるとか？",
      "startTime": 100.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　レッスンが大変なのは当たり前です！",
      "startTime": 101.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "私達、アイドルはファンのみなさんに最高のステージを\n観ていただくのが仕事ですから",
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それが分かっているなら、愛は立派なアイドルだよ\nだったら、これからも――",
      "startTime": 115.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、私は立派なんかじゃありません……\nダメダメなんです……",
      "startTime": 121.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "最近LizNoirの四人で通し稽古する機会があって\n改めて気付いたんです……",
      "startTime": 129.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "私はLizNoirにはいらない子なんだって……",
      "startTime": 131.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ、そんなことはない。愛とこころが\n加入して、LizNoirはより人気が出たんだろ？",
      "startTime": 139.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "海外での評価も高いじゃないか。愛はもう\nLizNoirには欠かせないメンバーに――",
      "startTime": 146.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "それは私じゃなくて、こころのお手柄です\nこころが強引に先輩方の考えを変えたからなんです",
      "startTime": 152.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "こころはお調子者かもしれませんが、しっかりキャラを\n立てて、LizNoirの新しい魅力を引き出しました",
      "startTime": 159.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんや葵さんのパフォーマンスのレベルの高さは\n言うまでもありません！　でも、私だけは……",
      "startTime": 167.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "私だけは、添え物なんです\nいなくてもいい子なんですよーっ！",
      "startTime": 174.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、莉央さんや葵、それにこころと）\n（個性の強いメンバーで構成されている）",
      "startTime": 181.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（愛だって充分魅力的な子なんだけど）\n（三人が強過ぎて、自信を失いかけてるんだ）",
      "startTime": 188.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "そんなわけで、ライブが始まる前に\n引退の意向をお伝えしようと……",
      "startTime": 195.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ。愛がいらないなんて、誰も思ってない\n君はLizNoirには不可欠な存在だ",
      "startTime": 202.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょうか……。このまま私が星見プロにいたら\nご迷惑がかかるんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 209.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "私のことだったら気にしないで下さい\n実家のラーメン屋を継ぎますから",
      "startTime": 214.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "これでも結構、麺上げはうまいって\n父も褒めてくれて――",
      "startTime": 220.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "愛、LizNoirには君が必要だ。それに君には\n間違いなくアイドルの才能がある",
      "startTime": 226.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
